{"tid":249345,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國泰大裁員 今先向總經理級別GM開刀","createTime":"2017-05-19T08:39:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-19T10:56:19.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"915e62255e885b77227e46f3cb15dcb43b647f2d","tid":249345,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T08:39:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170519/large/1495181569_1dcf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170519%2Flarge%2F1495181569_1dcf.jpg&h=c5fdda29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國泰航空計劃削減30%，市傳今日會向後勤員工進行大規模裁員。消息透露，國泰今日先向包括GM（總經理）在內的level E最高職級管理層「開刀」，多個部門都要削減或取消GM人手，以節省開支。另一波裁員行動則下周一（22日）進行，主要是level C（經理級）或以上的員工，牽涉部門包括營業及市務部、會計等。至於屬level A及B的後勤的基層員工也不能倖免，料將於6月裁員。"},{"pid":"613c20f1e83c156738c0179937b6aa6ce2d1466f","tid":249345,"uid":42250,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T08:41:42.000Z","msg":"賣二手空姐制服即刻轉虧為盈啦"},{"pid":"87b8ed53aed9cd532031d52c5586d1fecd78938f","tid":249345,"uid":29879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T08:42:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賣二手空姐制服即刻轉虧為盈啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5d997255fab8f7eeb3f1d1bb1e7393d944211cd","tid":249345,"uid":29602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T08:43:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>賣二手空姐制服即刻轉虧為盈啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"944af9b4060971e805035129402d47dee6081256","tid":249345,"u